Fight alongside Task Force 141 in a globe-trotting single-player campaign, play solo or rally with your team in immersive multiplayer combat, with new locales and ways to play. Experience an evolved Special Ops game mode featuring tactical co-op gameplay. 

Additionally look forward to Call of Duty: Warzone 2.0 releasing this year. Expect a massive calendar of free content post-launch featuring evolving gameplay with new maps, modes, seasonal events, community celebrations and more.

snippet.title: Official Reveal Trailer | Call of Duty: Modern Warfare
snippet.description:
Prepare to go dark, Modern Warfare is back!
 
The stakes have never been higher as players take on the role of lethal Tier One operators in a heart-racing saga that will affect the global balance of power. Call of Duty: Modern Warfare engulfs fans in an incredibly raw, gritty, provocative narrative that brings unrivaled intensity and shines a light on the changing nature of modern war. Developed by the studio that started it all, Infinity Ward delivers an epic reimagining of the iconic Modern Warfare series from the ground up.
 
In the visceral and dramatic single-player story campaign, Call of Duty: Modern Warfare pushes boundaries and breaks rules the way only Modern Warfare can. Players will engage in breathtaking covert operations alongside a diverse cast of international special forces throughout iconic European cities and volatile expanses of the Middle East.
 
And the story doesn’t end there.
 
In Call of Duty: Modern Warfare, players will be thrust into an immersive narrative spanning the entire game. Players can experience the ultimate online playground with classic multiplayer or squad-up and play cooperatively in a collection of elite operations, accessible to all skill levels.
 
Call of Duty: Modern Warfare arrives October 25th, 2019.

Follow #CallofDuty for the latest intel:
Twitter: http://twitter.com/CallofDuty
Instagram: http://instagram.com/callofduty
Facebook: http://facebook.com/CallofDuty

snippet.title: The History of the WORST GUNS in Call of Duty...
snippet.description:
The History of the WORST GUNS in Call of Duty…
Drop a LIKE for more Call of Duty stuff! (乃^o^)乃
Nifty Things Down Here ⇩

Today, we use the worst guns in every single Call of Duty game ever made!

…except for Big Red One, Call of Duty Online, and some other COD games that didn’t work

lol

I decided to do a challenge video AGAIN; play every Call of Duty game ever made in one video, and try to get as many kills as I can, but this time with the Worst Guns ever in each COD game!

This video includes gameplay and some of my opinions about Call of Duty, Call of Duty 2, Call of Duty 3, Call of Duty 4, Call of Duty: World at War, Modern Warfare 2, Black Ops 1, Modern Warfare 3, Black Ops 2, Call of Duty: Ghosts, Call of Duty: Advanced Warfare, Black Ops 3, Modern Warfare Remastered, Infinite Warfare, Call of Duty WW2, Black Ops 4, Modern Warfare 2019, Black Ops Cold War, COD Vanguard, and Call of Duty: Mobile! That’s 20 Call of Duty games in ONE video…WOW

All of this footage was captured on the Xbox 360, Xbox Series X and PS5 at 1080p 60fps and on PC at 4k 60fps so you can see all of the graphic and gameplay changes over time!

The guns of Call of Duty have changed a lot over time; from the Nambu to the Skorpion, there have been some BAD guns!

As usual, I’m really surprised with the results of this challenge video as well…

So, which COD gun do YOU think is the worst? Should I make more History of Call of Duty videos like this? Leave a comment letting me know! ^-^

This video includes gameplay and some of my opinions about Call of Duty, Call of Duty 2, Call of Duty 3, Call of Duty 4, Call of Duty: World at War, Modern Warfare 2, Black Ops 1, Modern Warfare 3, Black Ops 2, Call of Duty: Ghosts, Call of Duty: Advanced Warfare, Black Ops 3, Modern Warfare Remastered, Infinite Warfare, Call of Duty WW2, Black Ops 4, Modern Warfare 2019, Black Ops Cold War, COD Vanguard, and Call of Duty: Mobile! That’s 20 Call of Duty games in ONE video…WOW

All of this footage was captured on the Xbox 360, Xbox Series X and PS5 at 1080p 60fps and on PC at 4k 60fps so you can see all of the graphic and gameplay changes over time!

The guns of Call of Duty have changed a lot over time; from the Nambu to the Skorpion, there have been some BAD guns!

As usual, I’m really surprised with the results of this challenge video as well…

So, which COD gun do YOU think is the worst? Should I make more History of Call of Duty videos like this? Leave a comment letting me know! ^-^
